thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Vivian

author: Vivian
title: Vivian
text: Been dealing with OCVH Lakewood for a number of years. We find the care excellent and have also used their boarding facilities a few times. Clean modern location with a very friendly helpful staff. Would recommend them to anyone looking for top flite pet care.
